	<brief_description>
		Native singleton managing server-side rendering for railway tracks.
	</brief_description>
	<description>
		[TrackRenderingServer] is an engine singleton used by [MaszynaTrack3D] to manage track rendering directly through [RenderingServer]. It owns per-track render instances, uploads path data for GPU deformation, manages sleeper multimeshes, and generates rail and ballast meshes without adding helper nodes to the scene tree.
	</description>
